{
  "stem": "25809.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was just one open window, and an open space with a counter, and the butchers-- two or three butchers-- would be standing behind it.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Very simple, very simple-- some butcher blocks and that was it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Again, very difficult for me to realize how poor they were, or if they were poor.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody seemed well.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And everybody seemed in a reasonable good mood.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the typical Jewishness, I was not used to it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And because of this typical Jewishness, the, the, the dialects, the, the very Jewish words that were being spoken, the Yiddish that was being spoken, it was not an, an, an area of comfort for me.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I didn't feel that comfortable with it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And strangely enough, if I use-- sometimes when I talk to my daughter and I use a Yiddish expression, she will look at me and say, oh, come on, Dad.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Knock it off.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She doesn't like it, either.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I immediately translate that when I was in her shoes or at her age or whatever, I didn't like it either.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And somehow, this seems to have carried through in my daughter also.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She's not interested in the, the typical Jewish expressions or the, the, the Yiddish things, even though I sometimes-- I've learned over the years, of course, a fair amount of Yiddish words.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But I, I don't use them.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I use them very sparingly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of the ghetto?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Maybe there was an electricity in the air.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I am very sensitive to, to, to the way a, a room-- I can walk into a house, into a room, into an area.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Any area I walk into, I pick up vibrations.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's the word I was looking for.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
